sequenceDiagram
    participant Logs as Log Sources
    participant ES as Entity Store
    participant AC as Asset Criticality
    participant RE as Risk Engine
    participant UI as Security UI

    Note over ES: ESQL extracts entities<br/>from log sources
    Logs->>ES: Entity extraction (ESQL)
    ES->>ES: Transform aggregates to latest index
    ES->>ES: Enrich policy retains fields

    Note over RE: Scheduled task (1h default)
    RE->>RE: ESQL aggregation of alert risk scores
    AC->>RE: Criticality modifier applied
    RE->>RE: Persist to risk-score index
    RE->>RE: Latest transform updates

    UI->>ES: Query entity indices
    UI->>RE: Query risk score indices
    UI->>AC: Query criticality
